Class LoadCaseLabelInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • amesmarket.filereaders.LoadCaseLabelInfo

  • public class LoadCaseLabelInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Models all the different pieces of information that may show up in a label in on of the master/aux/scenario load case files.
